Summary: High flying green colored object making zig zag lines that disappeared before photo
divs: Sighting DetailsIn the Old Market with girlfriend and two friends at night. Looked up at it, and it was making zig zag lines for approximately three minutes. When tried to take a picture of it with a cell phone camera, it disappeared completely, leaving a green streak of light. During the time that it was zig zagging, it moved very quickly, but remained in one short space. Looked around for a few minutes afterward in all directions to try to relocate it, but could not find it or anything similar to it anywhere else in the visible sky.
